snippet.title: Rangoli Designs for Bhogi 2025 | Muggulu 7 Dots | Happy Pongal Kolam
snippet.description:
@SimpleRangoliDesigns  This tutorial will show you how to draw Rangoli Designs for Bhogi 2025 patterns using materials such as dry rice flour, colored sand or flower petals Rangoli designs by Aishwarya. Simple rangoli Pulli Kolam pattern is created on the floor in living rooms or courtyards. Draw the Lines step by step as it is shown in this video and will be awesome Rangoli Design.

😲 The Muggulu 7 Dots pattern here is one of the amazing latest kolam designs.

Simple Rangoli Designs and Happy Pongal Kolam by Aishwarya with dots for beginners and intermediate.

snippet.title: Bhogi Kundala muggulu 🌸Simple Pongal Pot Koalm rangoli🌸Sankranthi muggulu 2025 New designs Simple
snippet.description:
Bhogi Kundala muggulu 🌸Simple Pongal Pot Koalm rangoli🌸Sankranthi muggulu 2025 New designs Simple
It is our tradition to draw kolam every day morning at the doorsteps.
There are many benefits of drawing kolam in front of the house.
It is auspicious and believes Goddess Lakshmi enters the house if kolam is drawn.
Kolam brings a lot of positive vibrations and energy to you and your home.
Draw kolam soon after you wake up and then do your prayers.
Kolam or rangoli ( रंगोली  ) is a part of Indian culture and transferred from generation to the next generation.
This ancient art form is also called as muggulu in parts of South India like Andhra Pradesh and Telangana.
People draw different creative rangoli kolam designs using kolam powder or muggu pindi which is 
actually crushed Lime stone powder available in different parts of India.
There are different types of rangoli or kolam designs like dots kolam, sikku kolam, padi kolam, Margazhi kolam.
People draw special rangoli designs for Festivals like Sankranthi (Pongal), Diwali (Deepavali), Vijaya Dashami (Dasara).
Women create deepam rangoli or kolam designs during Diwali festival time, create very big and Dhanurmasam muggulu (Margazhi) for Sankranthi or Pongal festival.
It is a belief among the people that drawing muggulu in front of the house in the early morning soon after wake brings
good fortune to them and their family.
People mix rice flour to limestone powder and prepare their own kolam powder. Muggulu can also be drawn with rice flour only.
These Beautiful and creative designs are decorated with flowers based on the occasion or festival.

snippet.title: চাঁপাইনবাবগঞ্জ সীমান্তে টানা উত্তেজনা, স্লোগান; কী হয়েছিল দুই সীমান্তে? | BBC Bangla
snippet.description:
বাংলাদেশ-ভারত সীমান্তের একটি অংশে কাঁটাতারের বেড়া নির্মাণ নিয়ে তিন দিন ধরে একরকম টানাপড়েন বা উত্তেজনার পরিস্থিতি সৃষ্টি হয়েছে। চাঁপাইনবাবগঞ্জ এবং নওগাঁ জেলা সংলগ্ন সীমান্তের ভারতের দিকের অংশে বেড়া নির্মাণ নিয়ে বাংলাদেশ অংশ থেকে বাধা দেয়া হয়েছে। কী ঘটেছিল সেখানে? অর্চি অতন্দ্রিলার প্রতিবেদন 

*******************************************
বিবিসি নিউজ বাংলার ইউটিউব চ্যানেলে আপনাকে স্বাগতম। 
এখানে আপনি দেখতে পাবেন দেশ ও দেশের বাইরের সমসাময়িক গুরুত্বপূর্ণ ঘটনাবলী নিয়ে বস্তুনিষ্ঠ ও বিশ্লেষণধর্মী প্রতিবেদন, বিবিসি নিউজ বাংলার টিভি অনুষ্ঠান প্রবাহ এবং বাংলাদেশ ট্রেন্ডিং-এর সকল কন্টেন্ট। নিয়মিত ভিডিও আপডেট পেতে এবং অনুষ্ঠান দেখতে সাবস্ক্রাইব করতে ভুলবেন না!

snippet.title: Vishal உடன் படம் பார்த்த Varalaxmi ! Vishal reply to Health Issue | Vishal Speech
snippet.description:
Madha Gaja Raja is an upcoming Indian Tamil-language action comedy film directed by Sundar C and produced by Gemini Film Circuit. It stars Vishal, Anjali and Varalaxmi Sarathkumar in the leading roles, while Santhanam and Sonu Sood play other pivotal supporting roles. The film began production in 2012 and was completed by 2013, but remained unreleased for over a decade due to financial troubles. It is scheduled to release in theatres on 12 January 2025, during the Pongal weekend. Madha Gaja Raja Special Permiere Show happened in chennai today. The film began production in 2012 and was completed by 2013, but remained unreleased for over a decade due to financial troubles. It is scheduled to release in theatres on 12 January 2025, during the Pongal weekend. Madha Gaja Raja Special Permiere Show happened in chennai today. Episode 4292: Maa Ka Abhaas
--------------------------------------------------------
Sunder's mother feels that Champaklal might leave the country, while the Gokuldham residents work together to figure out the situation. Meanwhile, Inspector Pandey is tasked with urgently locating Champaklal.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4292 | 11 Jan 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Vyaah da Kalesh | Harshdeep Ahuja

Urban Theka: https://www.devilsclothing.urbantheka.in/

Vyaah Da Kalesh" 🎉🤣 – Dive into the madness of a Punjabi wedding where emotions, drama, and hilarity collide! Mummy, Daddy, and Robin are over the moon preparing for Blacky's big day, but you know how weddings in Punjabi families are – full of chaos, clashes, and non-stop fun! 💃🕺

From the overexcited mummy's shopping spree to daddy's budgeting troubles and Robin's quirky antics, this video captures all the kalesh that happens when the parivaar gears up for a wedding. 🥳💍

Will Blacky's wedding go smoothly, or will the kalesh steal the show? Watch till the end for laughter, love, and a whole lot of Punjabi vibes!

snippet.title: तिल-गुड़-मूंगफली के लड्डू-ठंड के लिये पौष्टिक मिठाई, स्वाद-सेहत व परंपरा की त्रिवेणी | Til Gud Laddu
snippet.description:
मकर संक्रान्ति स्पेशल, चिल्ला जाड़े के लिए पारंपरिक मिठास, Warm Your Heart and Soul with Til Gud Peanut Laddu, ठंड में इम्युनिटी बढ़ाने वाले तिल-गुड़ मूंगफली के लड्डू, 

#tilgudladdu #makarsankranti #laddu 

Ingredients for
Til Gud Peanuts Laddu
तिल - Sesame - 1 cup (150 grams)
मूंगफली - Peanuts - 1 cup (175 grams)
घी - Ghee - 3/4 cup
बादाम कतरन - Almond flakes - 1/2 cup (70 grams)
किशमिश - Raisins - 1/2 cup (70 grams)
गेहूं का आटा - Wheat flour - 2 cup (250 grams)
गुड़ - Jaggery - 500 grams
सोंठ - Dry ginger powder - 2 tsp
जायफल - Nutmeg powder - 1/2 tsp
इलाइची - Cardamom - 8-10 no, crushed
दूध - Milk - 2 tsp

Subscribe for more recipes - 
http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=nishamadhulika

For the Best recipes on YouTube, log onto - 
http://www.youtube.com/nishamadhulika

Visit my Hindi Website

snippet.title: Ramayana: The Legend Of Prince Rama | Official Hindi Trailer | 24th January
snippet.description:
रामायण: The Legend of Prince Rama in cinemas on January 24th, 2025 in English, Hindi, Tamil and Telugu! Trailer out now!

Prince Rama of Ayodhya must draw on his inner strength and gather allies to
rescue his beloved Sita when the demon king Ravan kidnaps her and imprisons
her in the kingdom of Lanka. A timeless tale of heroism and honour, this film is a
visual blend of Japanese and Indian animation traditions. Based on Valmiki’s
Ramayana.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Mannat Har khushi paane ki | Episode 1 | 06 January 25 | Mannat's special day
snippet.description:
📲 Download JioCinema: https://bit.ly/3Be09Z3

Mannat Har khushi paane ki | Episode 1 | 06 January 25

Sonia abandons her newborn, but Shruti rescues the baby girl from the seashore and names her Mannat. Twenty-three years later, Mannat dreams of becoming the world's best chef. Will her journey lead her to uncover the truth about her past?

-------------------

Abandoned as a newborn by her own heartless mother and raised by her resilient maasi, Shruti, Mannat grows up to be a passionate and ambitious chef, unaware of her mysterious origins. Her journey intertwines with that of Vikrant, a successful buisnessman (restaurateur), as they bond over their love for cooking amidst the vibrant backdrop of Mumbai's chawls and elite culinary spaces. Mannat’s biological mother is none other than Aishwarya, a wealthy and manipulative woman determined to keep her secrets buried who is also Mannat's boss at Mezbaani where she works as a junior chef. Life takes a dramatic turn when Mannat discovers Shruti is not her biological mother, propelling her on a desperate quest to save Shruti’s life by finding her real mother for a liver transplant. Amidst these revelations, Mannat finds her strongest support in Vikrant, the prince charming of her life, who stands by her side, offering unwavering encouragement as she navigates the challenges life throws her way. As Mannat’s rising career, Shruti’s failing health, and the revelations of a hidden past collide, Mannat faces a whirlwind of love, betrayal, and self-discovery. Will her dreams and resilience help her overcome the storm, or will the weight of her past keep her from achieving her destiny?
